{"title":"南口行","authors":["朱光"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南口行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城万里压高峦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见尘沙从北起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诺诺千山久作澜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官厅波映有奇观。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒山今已变青山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伫待深林成长日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三载辛勤云雾间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清溪南口放歌还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷锄日出向山隈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开辟梯条留沃土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩棘除荆废石堆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此生幸得此栽培。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纭农事向阳台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈日当空浇地急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔草留苗次第来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎泉灌溉几低徊。（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山花开放味芳浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜雪袭来南就食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未及忙忙采蜜蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春归辛苦蜜千钟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝晴暮雨昼偏长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳后方知餐不易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豆茁瓜肥斗嫩桑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜来泉湍入窗凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）向阳台是我们劳动生产的山名"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}